import React from 'react'; function AboutUs(){ return(

About us


Welcome to RentYug, your number one source for all things product to give or take on rent. We're dedicated to providing you the very best of product.


Founded in Feb 2021 by Sumit Dhakad with partnership of Ajay Patel and Aniket Verma, RentYug has come a long way from its beginnings in Bhopal, mp, India. Aniket Verma, Ajay Patel and Sumit Dhakad first started out, their passion for pocket-friendly products drove them to start their own business.


We hope you enjoy our services as much as we enjoy offering them to you. If you have any questions or comments, please don't hesitate to contact us.


Sincerely,


Ajay Patel

Aniket Verma

Sumit Dhakad
